(\varepsilon_{\rm F}\) reaching the top of the valence band. This latter picture is actually in qualitative agreement with recent photoemission measurements [25] of the Fermi level as a function of Mn concentration in Mn\({}_{x}\)Ga\({}_{1-x}\)As.
